he accidentally pressed the button.

297
00:15:02,881 --> 00:15:03,361
Yes.

298
00:15:03,680 --> 00:15:04,600
He probably had low blood sugar

299
00:15:04,800 --> 00:15:05,800
and his fingers were shivering.

300
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:07,960
It's been four years.

301
00:15:08,361 --> 00:15:08,800
Can you come up

302
