with a better excuse?

303
00:15:11,241 --> 00:15:12,161
It has been four years.

304
00:15:12,560 --> 00:15:13,401
We've been staying by your side
for the past four years

305
00:15:13,641 --> 00:15:14,720
as you repeatedly complained about him.

306
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:15,921
If you think

307
00:15:16,121 --> 00:15:16,840
you're still angry at him,

308
00:15:17,281 --> 00:15:18,200
why don't you take the project

309
00:15:18,480 --> 00:15:19,080
as a chance to torture him?

310
00:15:19,361 --> 00:15:21,401
Make him suffer.

311
00:15:21,800 --> 00:15:22,881
If I agree to work on this project,

312
00:15:23,121 --> 00:15:24,320
he'll be my client.

313
00:15:25,041 --> 00:15:26,121
If I am to torture him,

314
00:15:26,401 --> 00:15:26,960
