315
00:15:27,161 --> 00:15:28,440
I'll be the one suffering eventually.

316
00:15:32,080 --> 00:15:32,600
Jingjing.

317
00:15:33,680 --> 00:15:34,800
Do you remember the novel
Miss Chen wrote

318
00:15:35,041 --> 00:15:36,041
two years ago?

319
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:37,001
I do.

320
00:15:37,361 --> 00:15:38,241
My Breakthrough Youth.

321
00:15:38,761 --> 00:15:40,001
Many people commented,

322
00:15:40,121 --> 00:15:41,001
saying that it had a terrible ending.

323
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:41,921
It was because Miss Chen

324
00:15:42,080 --> 00:15:43,080
never bothered explaining in the novel,

325
00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:44,881
whether Lin Youmei and Chen Donglin

326
00:15:44,921 --> 00:15:46,080
ended up together.

327
00:15:47,440 --> 00:15:49,080
What does the terrible ending
have anything to do with me?

328
00:15:49,641 --> 00:15:51,080
Miss Chen mentioned this

329
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:51,680
during the previous gathering.

330
00:15:51,720 --> 00:15:53,080
You are Lin Youmei,

331
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:54,761
and Kang Jiawei is Chen Donglin.

332
00:15:55,921 --> 00:15:56,960
I'm done.

333
00:15:57,241 --> 00:15:57,761
I'm going to bed.

334
00:15:57,960 --> 00:15:58,560
I have to work tomorrow.

335
00:15:58,761 --> 00:15:59,521
You should go to bed earlier too.

336
00:15:59,840 --> 00:16:00,680
Keep it down.

337
00:16:02,761 --> 00:16:03,440
Stop running away

338
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:04,401
from it.

339
00:16:05,001 --> 00:16:06,281
I'm not running away from it.

340
00:16:06,680 --> 00:16:07,680
