344
00:16:11,001 --> 00:16:11,521
between us,

345
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:12,960
and interact with him professionally.

346
00:16:13,440 --> 00:16:14,200
I'm asked

347
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:14,960
