349
00:16:30,641 --> 00:16:31,320
Mr. Kang.

350
00:16:31,800 --> 00:16:32,641
This is

351
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:33,840
our current proposal

352
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:35,001
for the makeover of your place.

353
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:35,600
Amy.

354
00:16:36,121 --> 00:16:37,440
Mr. Kang, here's my proposal.

355
00:16:37,761 --> 00:16:38,600
Sorry. I have a question.

356
00:16:39,800 --> 00:16:40,361
Where is Xu Jingjing?

357
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:42,440
She's no longer in charge

358
00:16:42,641 --> 00:16:43,200
of this project.

359
00:16:43,560 --> 00:16:44,401
Amy is

360
00:16:44,641 --> 00:16:45,800
a very young and promising designer too.

361
00:16:47,401 --> 00:16:48,041
