362
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:49,041
directly?

363
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:52,560
I'm afraid that
she's at the police station now.

364
00:16:52,761 --> 00:16:53,440
It's about

365
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:54,401
the break-in at her place.

366
00:16:56,521 --> 00:16:57,361
Excuse me, Mr. Wei.

367
00:16:58,001 --> 00:16:58,641
Sorry, Miss Amy.

368
00:16:59,241 --> 00:16:59,680
I'm not trying

369
00:16:59,840 --> 00:17:00,680
to make things difficult for you.

370
00:17:01,161 --> 00:17:02,001
However,

371
00:17:02,440 --> 00:17:02,921
if Xu Jingjing is not handling

372
00:17:02,921 --> 00:17:03,761
this project,

373
00:17:04,881 --> 00:17:05,680
