374
00:17:17,841 --> 00:17:18,680
Xu Jingjing!

375
00:17:22,240 --> 00:17:22,680
Why did you turn down

376
00:17:22,841 --> 00:17:23,361
the project?

377
00:17:23,680 --> 00:17:24,361
Don't worry, sir.

378
00:17:24,641 --> 00:17:25,601
Amy is a very smart

379
00:17:25,921 --> 00:17:26,921
and professional designer too.

380
00:17:27,240 --> 00:17:27,960
Sir?

381
00:17:28,401 --> 00:17:29,440
Did you just refer to me as "sir"?

382
00:17:29,680 --> 00:17:30,200
You're our client, sir.

383
00:17:30,401 --> 00:17:31,401
It's just an honorific.

384
00:17:31,760 --> 00:17:32,520
