386
00:17:34,280 --> 00:17:35,121
What do you want?

387
00:17:36,121 --> 00:17:37,081
Were you at the police station?

388
00:17:38,480 --> 00:17:39,121
Did they catch the thief?

389
00:17:39,401 --> 00:17:40,081
It's none of your business.

390
00:17:40,480 --> 00:17:41,200
Xu Jingjing.

391
00:17:41,321 --> 00:17:42,081
Can you stop

392
00:17:42,240 --> 00:17:42,841
treating me like this?

393
00:17:43,200 --> 00:17:43,760
I have to get to work.

394
00:17:43,960 --> 00:17:44,881
Then, I'll see you
after you get off work.

395
00:17:45,760 --> 00:17:46,720
I don't have anything to say to you.

396
00:17:46,921 --> 00:17:47,561
But I do.

397
00:17:47,841 --> 00:17:48,881
I have a lot to tell you.

398
00:17:50,361 --> 00:17:51,401
One of those things is the fact
that I owe you an apology.

399
00:17:53,161 --> 00:17:53,841
Sorry.

400
00:17:55,081 --> 00:17:55,561
I shouldn't have

401
00:17:55,760 --> 00:17:56,321
blocked you.

402
00:17:56,921 --> 00:17:57,361
Great.

403
00:17:57,760 --> 00:17:58,680
Are you finished?

404
00:18:01,161 --> 00:18:02,200
I know it's hard for you to forgive me.

405
00:18:02,401 --> 00:18:02,841
You're wrong.

406
00:18:03,321 --> 00:18:04,161
You're forgiven.

407
00:18:05,680 --> 00:18:07,081
In fact, I forgave you a long time ago.

408
00:18:07,361 --> 00:18:07,921
I understand.

409
00:18:08,200 --> 00:18:09,321
Because that was
when Mr. Kang just passed away,

410
00:18:09,561 --> 00:18:10,801
so you needed a place
to vent your feelings.

411
00:18:11,081 --> 00:18:11,680
I understand.

412
00:18:11,960 --> 00:18:12,440
I really do.

413
00:18:15,921 --> 00:18:16,601
Xu Jingjing.

414
00:18:16,601 --> 00:18:17,361
Mr. Kang.

415
00:18:17,561 --> 00:18:18,321
It has been four years.

416
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:20,401
I have to carry on with my own life.

417
00:18:21,121 --> 00:18:21,881
Goodbye.

