00:19:17,520 --> 00:19:18,121
What should I tell Xu Jingjing

428
00:19:18,280 --> 00:19:19,361
to make her forgive me?

429
00:19:30,601 --> 00:19:31,240
Hey.

430
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:39,081
Welcome.

431
00:19:46,561 --> 00:19:47,921
You really turned out to be a detective.

432
00:19:49,161 --> 00:19:49,801
You look even more handsome now.

433
00:19:52,361 --> 00:19:53,161
Does being a detective

434
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:54,280
make me handsome?

435
00:19:55,561 --> 00:19:56,801
You haven't changed a bit.

436
00:19:57,841 --> 00:19:58,561
By the way,

437
00:19:59,321 --> 00:20:00,401
why did you ask me out?

438
00:20:01,680 --> 00:20:02,601
Have you met Xu Jingjing yet?

439
00:20:03,561 --> 00:20:04,361
I met her just now.

440
00:20:06,361 --> 00:20:07,040
Really?

441
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:09,601
It seems like

442
00:20:09,921 --> 00:20:10,480
you're pretty close.

443
00:20:10,841 --> 00:20:11,680
Yes, we are.

444
00:20:15,641 --> 00:20:17,881
How close are you?

445
00:20:18,280 --> 00:20:19,200
My girlfriend...

446
00:20:22,361 --> 00:20:23,161
She's a policewoman.

447
00:20:25,841 --> 00:20:28,000
My girlfriend is a policewoman.

448
00:20:29,841 --> 00:20:30,841
Gao.

449
00:20:32,081 --> 00:20:33,641
From where did you pick this trick?

450
00:20:34,280 --> 00:20:36,040
Why did you break your sentences?

451
00:20:42,081 --> 00:20:43,520
Have you heard about
the break-in at her place?

452
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:48,280
She didn't tell me the details.

453
00:20:48,841 --> 00:20:49,760
She lost her computer,

454
00:20:50,040 --> 00:20:50,801
a tablet,

455
00:20:51,361 --> 00:20:52,121
and a handbag.

456
00:20:53,361 --> 00:20:53,881
She told me

457
00:20:54,040 --> 00:20:55,280
the bag was really important to her.

458
00:20:56,040 --> 00:20:57,280
