to retrieve it.

459
00:20:57,881 --> 00:20:58,401
We informed her

460
00:20:58,440 --> 00:20:59,680
to collect her belongings today.

461
00:21:00,361 --> 00:21:01,321
We retrieved everything she lost,

462
00:21:01,801 --> 00:21:02,841
including the bag,

463
00:21:04,200 --> 00:21:05,520
but she didn't look too pleased either.

464
00:21:06,520 --> 00:21:07,200
Why?

465
00:21:07,760 --> 00:21:08,401
Something on the bag

466
00:21:08,401 --> 00:21:09,601
was missing.

467
00:21:13,841 --> 00:21:15,361
