477
00:21:33,561 --> 00:21:34,760
It's not that valuable,

478
00:21:34,960 --> 00:21:36,081
but can you please

479
00:21:36,240 --> 00:21:37,081
help me find it?

480
00:21:41,321 --> 00:21:42,520
The criminal was planning

481
00:21:42,641 --> 00:21:44,680
