500
00:22:28,520 --> 00:22:29,841
for relationship advice?

501
00:22:33,881 --> 00:22:35,200
The biggest issue

502
00:22:36,280 --> 00:22:37,361
is with you now.

503
00:22:53,841 --> 00:22:54,561
Xiaobai.

504
00:22:55,321 --> 00:22:56,881
Do you know where Xu Jingjing is
right now?

505
00:23:02,760 --> 00:23:03,480
Jingjing.

506
00:23:04,081 --> 00:23:05,520
You are quite drunk.

507
00:23:06,040 --> 00:23:06,720
I'm fine.

508
00:23:07,361 --> 00:23:08,161
I can keep drinking.

509
