How could he?

524
00:23:43,801 --> 00:23:44,641
He's too shameless.

525
00:23:45,401 --> 00:23:46,361
He didn't get in touch with you,

526
00:23:46,841 --> 00:23:48,121
but neither did you take the initiative.

527
00:23:49,161 --> 00:23:49,841
Forget it.

528
00:23:50,200 --> 00:23:51,440
