533
00:23:56,760 --> 00:23:57,280
Why would I do that?

534
00:23:57,561 --> 00:23:58,361
Yes. Why would she do that?

535
00:23:58,720 --> 00:24:00,121
It was Kang Jiawei's fault.

536
00:24:00,881 --> 00:24:02,240
I know it was his fault.

537
00:24:02,601 --> 00:24:03,401
However,

538
00:24:04,240 --> 00:24:04,801
if none of you is willing

539
00:24:04,801 --> 00:24:06,081
to take the first step,

540
00:24:06,760 --> 00:24:07,401
you will be stuck here

541
00:24:07,440 --> 00:24:08,641
forever.

542
00:24:09,720 --> 00:24:11,081
Do you want to be stuck here forever?

543
00:24:16,760 --> 00:24:18,081
Do you still have feelings
for Kang Jiawei?

544
00:24:21,040 --> 00:24:21,801
I...

545
00:24:22,760 --> 00:24:24,240
I want to drink.

546
00:24:27,680 --> 00:24:29,361
Let's keep drinking.

547
00:24:30,881 --> 00:24:31,960
I'll get you more beer.

548
00:24:32,280 --> 00:24:33,040
We haven't finished it yet.

549
00:24:33,401 --> 00:24:34,240
It won't be enough for you.

550
00:24:34,561 --> 00:24:35,200
I'll use the washroom.

551
00:24:35,520 --> 00:24:36,361
Be quick!

552
00:24:56,440 --> 00:24:57,161
Xiaobai.

553
00:24:58,240 --> 00:24:59,000
Tell you what.

554
00:24:59,680 --> 00:25:01,000
Let's keep drinking

555
00:25:01,601 --> 00:25:02,680
until we're all drunk.

556
00:25:03,601 --> 00:25:04,161
Pour me more beer.

557
00:25:05,440 --> 00:25:06,361
Hurry up.

558
00:25:18,841 --> 00:25:19,480
You...

559
00:25:24,401 --> 00:25:25,121
Cheers!

560
00:25:45,280 --> 00:25:46,280
Why are you here?

561
00:25:53,440 --> 00:25:54,520
So you still care about me.

562
00:25:56,601 --> 00:25:57,960
You have so much confidence in yourself.

563
00:26:04,161 --> 00:26:05,121
Gao Zhan told me everything.

564
00:26:07,520 --> 00:26:08,960
When you were collecting
